msgstr "Cancelar escaneado"

#. Translators: Informing user the process was terminated
#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:441
msgid "Scanning process terminated!"
msgstr "Proceso de escaneado finalizado"

#. Translators: Asking user to enter the PDF password
#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:453
msgid "Enter your password"
msgstr "Ingresa tu contraseña"

#. Add-on summary/title, usually the user visible name of the add-on
#. Translators: Summary/title for this add-on
#. to be shown on installation and add-on information found in add-on store
#: buildVars.py:21
msgid "TesseractOCR: An OCR add-on"
msgstr "TesseractOCR: un complemento de OCR"

#. Add-on description
#. Translators: Long description to be shown for this add-on on add-on information from add-on store
#: buildVars.py:24
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Performs OCR on the selected image file, PDF, JPG, TIF, etc, or  a "
#| "document through a scanner and also can get the text from an accessible "
#| "PDF file.\n"
#| "The results are shown in a text file.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Windows+Control+r - Performs OCR to the selected image file\n"
#| "Windows+Control+w - Scans and recognize the document in the scanner\n"
#| "Windows+Control+t - To get the text from an accessible PDF\n"
msgid ""
"Performs OCR on the selected image file, PDF, JPG, TIF, etc, or  a document "
"through a scanner and also can get the text from an accessible PDF file.\n"
"The results are shown in a text file.\n"
"\n"
"Windows+Control+r - Performs OCR to the selected image file\n"
"Windows+Control+w - Scans and recognize the document in the scanner\n"
"Windows+Control+t - To get the text from an accessible PDF"
msgstr ""
"Realiza OCR sobre el archivo de imagen seleccionado, PDF, JPG, TIF, etc, o "
"un documento a través de un escáner y también puede obtener el texto de un "
"archivo PDF accesible.\n"
"Los resultados se muestran en un archivo de texto.\n"
"\n"
"Windows+Control+r - Realiza el OCR al archivo de imagen seleccionado\n"
"Windows+Control+w - Escanea y reconoce el documento en el escáner\n"
"Windows+Control+t - Obtiene el texto de un PDF accesible\n"

#. Brief changelog for this version
#. Translators: what's new content for the add-on version to be shown in the add-on store
#: buildVars.py:34
msgid ""
"Set compatibility with NVDA 2026.1.\n"
"Updated TesseractOCR to 5.5.0.\n"
"Updated XPDF to 4.0.6.\n"
"It is again possible to choose the scanner to use.\n"
"With Tesseract 5.5 the image orientation is automatically made by "
"Tesseract.\n"
"So, the document type \"Only paper orientation\" only announce the "
"orientation of the image.\n"
" Now, it only runs on 64-bits machines.\n"
" Some bugs were corrected."
msgstr ""

